cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SI, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the challenges faced by Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) in time series forecasting and proposes a solution by redefining the DNN model and considering data pre-processing, network architecture, and network parameters. This falls under the category of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Deep Recurrent Neural Network (DRNN) also suggests the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). The paper also deals with image classification, which falls under Computer Vision (cs.CV) and the use of time series data in socio-economic environments suggests Social and Information Networks (cs.SI).
